                   Nouveau si\u00e8ge social de Co-operators\u00a0\u00a0                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Le nouveau si\u00e8ge social de Co-operators, situ\u00e9 au 101 Cooper Drive, \u00e0 Guelph,&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    June 16, 2023                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/fr\/vitrine\/vitrine-du-batiment-durable\/profils-de-batiments-durables\/jacques-parizeau-bcz-p\/\">\n                                        L&#8217;\u00c9difice Jacques-Parizeau                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    La certification BCZ-Performance orientera les futurs projets d\u2019Ivanho\u00e9 Cambridge Situ\u00e9 au c\u0153ur du&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    May 29, 2023                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/fr\/vitrine\/vitrine-du-batiment-durable\/profils-de-batiments-durables\/le-phenix\/\">\n                                        Le Ph\u00e9nix                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Le Ph\u00e9nix se distingue une nouvelle fois et obtient la certification B\u00e2timent \u00e0&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    April 28, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/fr\/vitrine\/vitrine-du-batiment-durable\/profils-de-batiments-durables\/edifice_nx_du_college_humber\/\">\n                                        L\u2019\u00e9difice NX du Coll\u00e8ge Humber                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n  